entry.title: Sage Kitchen Cart With Cupboard
entry.summary:
Vendor: CorLiving
Type: KNT15XC
Price: 584.00

Description

  • Classic finish with natural wood finished top
  • Open and closed storage for convenience
  • Locking castors to keep cart in your desired space
  • Solid Rubberwood top is durable and easy to wipe clean
  • Towel bar allows for easy maneuvering and storage
  • Pinewood legs add durability and stability
  • Easy assembly

Compact kitchen? No problem! Add extra space to work, serve, and stow away kitchen accessories with this must-have kitchen cart. Its frame is clean-lined and showcases a classic finish to fit in any home's aesthetic. The top has a neutral wood grain finish and the pinewood legs are supported by four wheels with locking castors so your cart stays in the location of your choosing or can be moved at any time. With open and closed storage from the drawer to the cabinet, towel rack, and shelf you have ample space to keep all your kitchen necessities within arms reach.

Specifications

Assembly Required Yes
Product Dimensions 35"H X 32"W X 18"D
Product Weight 57 lbs.
Carton Shipping Dimensions 8"H X 35"W X 21"D
Carton Shipping Weight 63 lbs.
Materials Engineered wood, wood, metal
Max Weight 55 lbs.
